name: FSL__Work_Rule__c

fields.inlineHelpText: The object containing the custom field that's used for the count.

fields.name: FSL__CountType__c

Otherwise, compare the Minimum Crew Size to the Crew Size field on the Service Crew.

fields.inlineHelpText: The API name of the custom field on the count object.

fields.inlineHelpText: A numeric field on the service resource to count against.

fields.inlineHelpText: The service appointment lookup field that you're matching
